{"tid":2002124,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"胡鴻釣、牙fred、菊梓喬、周柏豪等一線紅星最新歌曲《再出發》你哋聽咗未呀？","createTime":"2020-05-05T04:25:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T17:31:56.000Z","uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a4be1b6c7a5f4fbb490fba5c18c130120e490f1e","tid":2002124,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:25:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=gwyb-NNONlY&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1%26v%3Dgwyb-NNONlY%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktYm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=d2016ee0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=gwyb-NNONlY&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n由前特首董建華、梁振英牽頭嘅「香港再出發大聯盟」，今日會喺位於中環嘅辦公室舉行記招宣布成立，並會發表共同宣言。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大聯盟搵咗歌手周柏豪、菊梓喬、鄭俊弘、泳兒、胡鴻鈞等人合唱</strong></span></span>，由鍾鎮濤作曲，簡嘉明填詞，總策劃包括全國政協委員黃英豪。部分歌詞提到「在最初同行/以後更應同行&hellip;&hellip;今放低紛爭/齊創新珍惜興建」等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8MQpf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8MQpf.jpg&h=edf42e11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfda18dbed7f14cfa5fad1bc465ff04bb2890b24","tid":2002124,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27018594acb43b60cf59a8cefd4c4a6e2aecb22b","tid":2002124,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:26:47.000Z","msg":"好可憐"},{"pid":"83b92c097bf2f40a96e40915847dc98cec3d44d4","tid":2002124,"uid":201299,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T04:27:10.000Z","msg":"聽左 好聽"},{"pid":"0afa88579517ab0a9987f484f271851e8bbbec9b","tid":2002124,"uid":346057,"l